<html lang='en'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1' />
    <title>New Login Detected | Note Taking App</title>
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f5f7fa; /* --color-system-neutral-50 */
        font-family:
          'Inter',
          -apple-system,
          BlinkMacSystemFont,
          'Segoe UI',
          Roboto,
          sans-serif;
        color: #232530; /* --color-system-neutral-800 */
        line-height: 1.5;
      }

      .email-container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 32px auto;
        background-color: #ffffff; /* --color-system-neutral-0 */
        border-radius: 16px; /* --radius-16 */
        box-shadow: 0px 8px 12px 0px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); /* --shadow-large */
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .header {
        background-color: #ffffff; /* --color-system-neutral-0 */
        padding: 32px; /* --spacing-400 */
        text-align: center;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e4ea; /* --color-system-neutral-200 */
      }

      .header-logo {
        color: #335cff; /* --color-system-blue-500 */
        font-size: 24px; /* --text-preset-1 */
        font-weight: 700;
        margin: 0 0 16px 0;
      }

      .security-alert {
        background-color: #ffd5d8; /* --color-system-red-100 */
        border-left: 4px solid #fb3748; /* --color-system-red-500 */
        padding: 16px; /* --spacing-200 */
        border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0; /* --radius-8 */
        margin: 0 0 24px 0; /* --spacing-300 */
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 12px; /* --spacing-150 */
      }

      .alert-icon {
        color: #fb3748; /* --color-system-red-500 */
        font-size: 20px;
        font-weight: bold;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 0 32px 32px; /* --spacing-400 */
      }

      .title {
        font-size: 20px; /* --text-preset-2 */
        line-height: 24px; /* --text-preset-2--line-height */
        letter-spacing: -0.5px; /* --text-preset-2--letter-spacing */
        font-weight: 700; /* --text-preset-2--font-weight */
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 24px; /* --spacing-300 */
      }

      p {
        font-size: 14px; /* --text-preset-4 */
        line-height: 16.8px; /* --text-preset-4--line-height */
        letter-spacing: -0.2px; /* --text-preset-4--letter-spacing */
        font-weight: 500; /* --text-preset-4--font-weight */
        color: #525866; /* --color-system-neutral-600 */
        margin-bottom: 16px; /* --spacing-200 */
      }

      .info-card {
        background-color: #f5f7fa; /* --color-system-neutral-50 */
        border-radius: 8px; /* --radius-8 */
        padding: 16px; /* --spacing-200 */
        margin: 24px 0; /* --spacing-300 */
      }

      .info-row {
        display: flex;
        margin-bottom: 12px; /* --spacing-150 */
      }

      .info-label {
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #2b303b; /* --color-system-neutral-700 */
        min-width: 120px;
      }

      .info-value {
        font-weight: 500;
        color: #525866; /* --color-system-neutral-600 */
      }

      .action-buttons {
        display: flex;
        gap: 16px; /* --spacing-200 */
        margin-top: 32px; /* --spacing-400 */
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 12px 24px; /* --spacing-150 --spacing-300 */
        border-radius: 8px; /* --radius-8 */
        font-size: 14px; /* --text-preset-4 */
        font-weight: 600; /* --text-preset-4--font-weight */
        transition: all 0.2s ease;
        text-align: center;
        flex: 1;
        min-width: 150px;
      }

      .btn-primary {
        background-color: #335cff; /* --color-system-blue-500 */
        color: #ffffff !important;
      }

      .btn-primary:hover {
        background-color: #2547d0; /* --color-system-blue-700 */
      }

      .btn-secondary {
        background-color: #f5f7fa; /* --color-system-neutral-50 */
        color: #525866 !important; /* --color-system-neutral-600 */
        border: 1px solid #e0e4ea; /* --color-system-neutral-200 */
      }

      .btn-secondary:hover {
        background-color: #e0e4ea; /* --color-system-neutral-200 */
      }

      .footer {
        padding: 24px 32px; /* --spacing-300 --spacing-400 */
        background-color: #f5f7fa; /* --color-system-neutral-50 */
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 12px; /* --text-preset-6 */
        line-height: 14.4px; /* --text-preset-6--line-height */
        color: #717784; /* --color-system-neutral-500 */
        border-top: 1px solid #e0e4ea; /* --color-system-neutral-200 */
      }

      .footer-links {
        margin-top: 8px; /* --spacing-100 */
      }

      .footer-links a {
        color: #335cff; /* --color-system-blue-500 */
        text-decoration: none;
        margin: 0 8px; /* --spacing-100 */
      }

      @media (max-width: 620px) {
        .email-container {
          margin: 16px; /* --spacing-200 */
          border-radius: 12px; /* --radius-12 */
        }

        .header,
        .content {
          padding: 24px; /* --spacing-300 */
        }

        .action-buttons {
          flex-direction: column;
          gap: 12px; /* --spacing-150 */
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='email-container'>
      <div class='header'>
        <div class='header-logo'>Note Taking App</div>
        <div class='security-alert'>
          <div class='alert-icon'>!</div>
          <div>Security alert: New login detected</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class='content'>
        <h2 class='title'>New access to your account</h2>

        <p>We detected a new login to your Note Taking App account. See details below:</p>

        <div class='info-card'>
          <div class='info-row'>
            <span class='info-label'>Account:</span>
            <span class='info-value'>{{email}}</span>
          </div>
          <div class='info-row'>
            <span class='info-label'>Date & time:</span>
            <span class='info-value'>{{loginTime}}</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p>If you recognize this activity, no action is required.</p>

        <p><strong>Wasn't you?</strong> Your account may be compromised. We recommend:</p>
        <ol>
          <li>Change your password immediately</li>
          <li>Review suspicious activity</li>
          <li>Enable two-factor authentication</li>
        </ol>

        <div class='action-buttons'>
          <a href='{{accountSettingsUrl}}' class='btn btn-primary'>Review Activity</a>
          <a href='{{passwordResetUrl}}' class='btn btn-secondary'>Change Password</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class='footer'>
        <p>This is an automated security notification. For security reasons, please don't reply to
          this email.</p>
        <p>Â© {{currentYear}} Note Taking App. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>